name: Human JukeBox SWAC Showdown
description:
A classic swac showdown! 

Play as the illustrious Southern University and A&M College's Human JukeBox and defeat your competition, other members of the Southwestern Athletic Conference.

Or.......better known as the SWAC!

Controls: Launch~ space bar, up arrow, or W/S key; Left~A key or left arrow; Right right arrow, or D key.

Get to 100 points without getting hit 10 times to win!

Photo/audiocredit: JukeBoxMedia, interactive socials in right corner of game.

DOWNLOAD IS FREE,  just hit "no thanks, just take me to the downloads"
